column1: I’ll have you know that this is the true strength of Gensokyo!
I must say that Gensokyo really is an interesting place,
though it is quite unfortunate that I must leave right away.
Thanks to you, we've had a lot on our plates.
At last, this incident has finally come to an end.
We didn’t sleep for an entire night.
Well, I guess it’s about time for me to return to the Hermit World too.
perhaps fate one day will allow our paths to cross again.
